    "bio": "An automation enthusiast, I help operations, sales, and marketing teams as well as founders, solopreneurs, freelancers, and growing businesses to streamline workflows and automate processes using n8n.\n\n🚀 Need custom automation?\nUse the link below to book your initial consultation and let's build something powerful together.",
